{"tid":1925001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼佬冇罩，咁不如上Twitter推廣下K Kwong隻DIY MASK","createTime":"2020-03-14T05:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T01:31:12.000Z","uid":127611,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7f06e6487a931f44f7258901d1c7039b3c04949e","tid":1925001,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"頭先見篇鬼佬新聞向鬼佬講點解香港人戴罩既原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/5799964/coronavirus-face-mask-asia-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5799964%2Fcoronavirus-face-mask-asia-us%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCa3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=5d9b9821\" target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/5799964/coronavirus-face-mask-asia-us/</a><br />\n隨住疫情愈黎愈嚴重，相信啲死唔撚戴既鬼佬對戴罩呢樣野都會開始重視<br />\n但問題係而家外國啲罩好多一早就比中國人搶哂<br />\n產能又唔夠，想買都買唔到<br />\n咁不如我地就上去Twitter同Reddit推廣K Kwong隻diy mask，講明香港人發明，作為冇罩下既替代品<br />\n<a href=\"https://diymask.site/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiymask.site%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCa3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=957abc88\" target=\"_blank\">https://diymask.site/</a><br />\n<br />\n幫到鬼佬之如，仲可以當做香港人既正向文宣<br />\n跟住順手可以帶出中國人點散播疫情，<br />\n講下佢地點唔比罩出口，隱瞞疫情，幫手煽風點火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9e85f19d8b0e03d9eb4ef18e4a18b36a93b44c","tid":1925001,"uid":101756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"一齊傳去外國，唔好比支那做戲攞哂威"},{"pid":"5a50e1a4d2c5d40e7af01ffc6c919fc8d6ab69f5","tid":1925001,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:50:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91aed6a18e388c51a2ef38872bb1b8f15c1205ad","tid":1925001,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69409f4f243707b4800a174e3c163cfa9574c38d","tid":1925001,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-